<p>Check out Mullenweg&#8217;s WCEU 2017 interview below to see the live demo of Gutenberg and make sure to take a few minutes to <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/gutenberg/" target="_blank">install the plugin</a> to see it in action for yourself.</p>
